LAN Connectors
---------------

**LAN (RJ45) connector** provides Ethernet connectivity over standardized Ethernet cables as shown in the figure below. The integrated |LAN| interface supports up to 1 Gbps data throughput.

The LAN0 port supports **optional** Power over Ethernet (PoE) feature.

.. rst-class:: text-center

    |LAN_img|

    *RJ45 LAN Connector*

.. note::

   Use CAT5 or better cables to achieve full data throughput over maximum distance defined by the 1000BASE-T standard (100m).